=== Details ===

The '''Token Collector''' is a type of battle item. It temporarily boosts the drop rate of [[Dungeon Tokens]] by 50% for 30 seconds.

=== Description ===

+50% Bonus to [[Dungeon Tokens]] gained.

=== Acquisition ===
{{ItemPrice/head‎|Battle items}}
{{ItemPrice|[[Dungeons|Dungeon Drop]]|Random}}
{{ItemPrice|[[Towns_%26_Cities#Kanto_Cities_.26_Towns|Pewter City]]|{{pdollar}}1,000}}
{{ItemPrice|[[Towns_%26_Cities#Hoenn_Cities_.26_Towns|Lilycove City]]|{{pdollar}}1,000}}
{{ItemPrice|[[Towns_%26_Cities#Sinnoh_Cities_.26_Towns|Veilstone City]]|{{pdollar}}1,000}}
{{ItemPrice|[[shops|Poké Mart]]|{{pdollar}}1,000}}
|}
|}

== Trivia ==
* In PokéClicker Beta, the Token Collector used a different sprite.

